seo: 用友U9,任意文件上传漏洞,插件,检测
seo_en: Yonyou U9, arbitrary file upload vulnerability, plugin, detection
summary: 该插件用于检测用友U9系统中是否存在任意文件上传漏洞，通过向PatchFile.asmx接口发送特定请求来验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether there is an arbitrary file upload vulnerability in the Yonyou U9 system, by sending a specific request to the PatchFile.asmx interface to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
